sub_title: Account Relationship Manager at Palo Alto
summary:
Excellent sales management with a proven record of success in delivering IT solutions. 
Expert in connecting business to the latest technologies with good knowledge of products variety and solutions complexity. Building and developing successful relationships with corporations and organizations key decision makers, direct sales and corporate re-sellers. Well experience with the marketplace capabilities and generating new business opportunities.

Specialties:
Accounts management, business development management and product management.
Managing Channels relationship; either for end-users or partners.
Identifying and qualifying new opportunities.
Selling and promoting the solutions of software, hardware, networking, security and cloud services.
The ability to prepare technical and services solutions proposals. Besides, the financial part of costing analysis. 
Excellent presentations performance.
Create and increase prospectsâ€™ needs and building solutions value.
Deals Closing.
Marketing strategies, campaigns and techniques. In addition to developing marketing material using multi software interactive platforms.
